in python tamplate class allow us to creat simplified syntax for output specification.


example:-
        from tring inport Tamplate
        t=Tamplate("my name is $name i live in $address")
        print(t.substitute({'name':'naushad warsi','address':"pune"}))
        
        
        
example2:-
          from string import Template
          student=[('nak',1),('mihir',20),('tahir',30)]
          t=Template('i am $name my roll number $roll')
          for i in student:
                  print(t.substitute(name=i[0],roll=i[1]))
